ers |date=13 March 2020 |accessdate=16 March 2020}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"63GlJ\">{{cite web |url=https://thehill.com/changing-america/sustainability/environment/488286-italys-coronavirus-lockdown-shows-what-nature |title=As Italy quarantines over coronavirus, swans appear in Venice canals, dolphins swim up playfully |author=Srikanth, Anagha |work=The Hill |date=18 March 2020 |accessdate=20 March 2020}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"9mMFi\">{{cite news |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/13/coronavirus-could-weaken-climate-change-action-hit-clean-energy.html |title=Coronavirus could weaken climate change action and hit clean energy investment, researchers warn |author=Newburger, Emma |publisher=[[CNBC]] |date=13 March 2020 |accessdate=16 March 2020}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"pH2jp\">{{cite web |url=https://text.npr.org/s.php?sId=820268157 |title=Text-Only NPR.org : Climate Change Push Fuels Split On Coronavirus Stimulus |publisher=NPR}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"dEHl9\">{{cite web |url=https://www.iea.org/commentaries/put-clean-energy-at-the-heart-of-stimulus-plans-to-counter-the-coronavirus-crisis |title=Put clean energy at the heart of stimulus plans to counter the coronavirus crisis\u2014Analysis |website=IEA}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"C3vSo\">{{Cite news |url=https://fortune.com/2020/03/10/coronavirus-remote-flexible-work-from-home/ |title=Commentary: Coronavirus may finally force businesses to adopt workplaces of the future |website=[[Fortune (magazine)|Fortune]]}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"Foevb\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/26/business/coronavirus-businesses.html |title=1,000 Workers, Go Home: Companies Act to Ward Off Coronavirus |first=David |last=Yaffe-Bellany |date=26 February 2020 |work=[[The New York Times]]}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=\"jRX9D\">{{cite news |title=Discarded coronavirus masks clutter Hong Kong's beaches, trails |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-hongkong-environme/discarded-coronavirus-masks-clu