a KML/Kentucky Route 89}}}}\n|map_custom=yes\n|map_notes=KY 89 highlighted in red\n|alternate_name=\n|length_mi=73.355\n|length_round=3\n|length_ref=<ref name=KYTC>{{cite web|url=http://apps.transportation.ky.gov/DMI_Reports/Official_MP_RL_params.aspx|title=Official DMI Route Log|last=Commonwealth of Kentucky|accessdate=28 December 2012}}</ref>\n|established=\n|direction_a=South\n|terminus_a=[[Image:Elongated circle 490.svg|25px]] [[Kentucky Route 490|KY 490]] near [[Livingston, Kentucky|Livingston]]\n|junction={{Plainlist|\n* {{Jct|state=KY|US|421}} by [[McKee, Kentucky|McKee]]\n* {{Jct|state=KY|US|60}} in [[Winchester, Kentucky|Winchester]]\n}}\n|direction_b=North\n|terminus_b=[[Image:Elongated circle 627.svg|25px]] [[Kentucky Route 627|KY 627]] in Winchester\n|counties=[[Rockcastle County, Kentucky|Rockcastle]], [[Jackson County, Kentucky|Jackson]], [[Estill County, Kentucky|Estill]], [[Clark County, Kentucky|Clark]]|previous_type=KY\n|previous_route=88\n|next_type=KY\n|next_route=90\n}}\n'''Kentucky Route 89''' ('''KY 89''') is a {{convert|73.355|mi|km|adj=mid|-long}} north\u2013south two-lane [[state highway]] that runs from [[Kentucky Route 490]] east of [[Livingston, Kentucky|Livingston]] to [[Kentucky Route 627]] in [[Winchester, Kentucky|Winchester]] in the [[U.S. state]] of [[Kentucky]]. The highway goes though [[McKee, Kentucky|McKee]], [[Irvine, Kentucky|Irvine]].\n\nThe route intersects with [[U.S. Route 421 (Kentucky)|U.S. Route 421]], [[Kentucky Route 52]], [[Kentucky Route 499]], [[Kentucky Route 974]], and [[U.S. Route 60 in Kentucky|U.S. Route 60]].\n\n==Major intersections==\n{{KYinttop|length_ref=<ref name=KYTC/>}}\n{{KYint\n|county=Rockcastle\n|mile=0.000\n|location=none\n|road={{jct|state=KY|KY|490|name1=S Upper River Road}}\n|notes=Southern terminus\n}}\n{{KYint\n|county=Jackson\n|cspan=4\n|location=none\n|mile=8.903\n|road={{jct|state=KY|KY|2002|dir1=south}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of KY 2002\n}}\n{{KYint\n|location=none\n|mile=18.860\n|roa